    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there, neighbor! It truly breaks my heart to let this beauty go, but it\u2019s time for her to find a new home. I\u2019ve absolutely babied this car since day one\u2014always garaged and kept in stunning, showroom-quality shape. Driving it feels like a dream, and honestly, you\u2019d be hard-pressed to find another one this clean around town. She\u2019s been my pride and joy, and I know you're going to fall in love the moment you see her. She\u2019s practically perfect and ready for a new adventure!",
