    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering a superlative example of precision engineering, this unit features the legendary S54 inline-six, recently treated to a comprehensive top-end overhaul. We've addressed the critical VANOS system with Beisan viton seals and performed a meticulous valve clearance adjustment to optimize the torque curve and ensure peak volumetric efficiency. The chassis rigidity is unsurpassed, having undergone proactive subframe reinforcement with structural plates to mitigate torsional stress. Power is delivered through a crisp 6-speed manual gearbox to a limited-slip differential with a 3.62 final drive ratio, providing exceptional mechanical grip and exit speeds. The suspension geometry has been recalibrated with high-durometer bushings and adjustable coilover dampening to minimize body roll and maximize contact patch consistency. This is a turn-key, high-performance machine maintained to a standard that exceeds factory specifications.",
      "price": 48950.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 27
    },
    {
