    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m honestly a bit heartbroken to let this beauty go, but it\u2019s time for her to find a new home. I\u2019ve treated this car like a member of the family\u2014always garaged, hand-washed every Sunday, and kept in absolutely stunning condition. It looks and drives just like it did the day it rolled off the lot. You won\u2019t find a speck of dust in the cabin or a single hiccup under the hood. It\u2019s truly a showroom-quality ride that\u2019s ready for your next weekend adventure. Swing by, let\u2019s grab a coffee, and I\u2019ll show you why this is the one you\u2019ve been waiting for!",
